column5: Hi to all the fishing nuts out there. 2007 been good year for me, but the fishing not so good. Did some fishing last Fri. at Gilford. A lot of small perch, we kept about 26. Hope this year we bring you all trophy winners.
Hi back.....may your next fishing adventure be your best.....nice to meet you
....Well Lord tunder'n, bout time you got on board Gary.    So when's perch dinner? and remember "Post count is NOT a sign of intelligence", suposedly it's the content that counts?
Welcome aboard!  There can never be too many Gary's, no matter how you spell it...grin. Garry2rs
